page.title: 12School Life
page.content:
My day begins at 7.15a.m. I go into the bathroom, wash, and clean my teeth. Then I get dressed, go downstairs and have my breakfast. School starts at 9.00a.m. We have registration and then go into assembly. After, we go into our classrooms and do maths until playtim When we come in, we do English. Lunch is at noon. We restart at 1.00p.m. when we come in we do art or My Body Project. We finish school at 3.30p.m. I walk home with Alison, Tracy, Nicole, Kelly, and Eloise. When I get home I either watch T.V. or play with the computer. After tea I play with Alison, watch T.V., and go to my bedroom. I read before going to sleep at 10.00p.m.
Catherine Davies.
